<h2>Our Story</h2>
<p>During the summer of 2007, my great friend Peter and I decided to embark on an ambitious journey: to travel around Bulgaria's entire Black Sea coast, document every major beach destination, and create a comprehensive online guide that would help travelers discover the beauty of Bulgarian beaches.</p>

<p>We spent weeks exploring the 378-kilometer coastline from Durankulak in the north to Rezovo in the south. Armed with cameras and a sense of adventure, we visited 46 distinct beach locations, capturing thousands of photographs and gathering firsthand information about each destination.</p>

